  "texts": [
    "ALIGNTRANSFORMER [30] is a radiology report generation model to alleviate the data bias problem and model the very long sequence.",
    "Knowledge Matters [31] is a novel radiology generation framework assisted by general and specific knowledge.",
    "Meshed-Memory Transformer [32] is a simple but effective progressive text generation model to produce the radiology report by incorporating high-level concepts into the generation progress.",
    "Reinforcement Learning Over a Cross-Modal Memory (CMM-RL) [33] is an enhanced radiology report generation model with reinforced cross-modal alignment to alleviate the requirement of annotated supervision while facilitating interactions across modalities.",
    "Cross-Modal Contrastive Attention (CMCA) [34] is a novel model to capture both visual and semantic information from similar cases."
